</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-author-date" -->
<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>Yup, Emotional storms and unskillful decisions.  Same.  Which is why we are probably never finished.  What would be the fun in that?</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
