<p>Great summary of the work and process, Carla. It is always in place for a structured overview and summary of the basics. Thanks for that.</p><p>This work is truly amazing. Centuries or even melleniums of human search is slowly coming to an end before our very eyes in the form of a harmless look at ourselves.</p>
