<span class="forum-post-template-date-only"><!--1504201670-->Thursday, August 31, 2017 at 10:47</span> 
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-author-date" -->
<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>Yes, that's what we see too. I don't think anyone has ever actually seen, before now, that the cause of all purely psychological misery is a single one. And it's human. It's not the devil, or sin, or anything metaphysical. One cause, one cure. One cause: the fear of life. One cure: look at yourself. Simple!</p>
