<div class="forum-post-quote"><p class="forum-post-quoted-name">Satishmuley</p><p style="margin-top:0;">Satsang means Sat (Truth) Sang (Company). In the company of truth.  my opinion Just1look is another name for Satsang. This is the real Satsang without external help.</p><p>Satish</p></div><p>You're totally right, Satish! We stopped calling our meetings satsang a few years ago, because we wanted to shed all spiritual concepts and ideas and get to the true core of the Self-Inquiry of Ramana Maharshi and satsang. What you said is true: Just One Look is Satsang in its cleanest form. You got it! Thank you!</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
